column6: ['Airbnb is a global travel community that offers end-to-end trips, including where you stay, what you do and the people you meet. Valued at over $30 Billion.', 'Stripe builds economic infrastructure for the internet. Businesses of every size—from new startups to public companies—use their software to accept payments and manage their businesses online. Valued at over $20 Billion.', 'Cruise is building autonomous vehicles to safely connect people to the places, things, and experiences they care about. Acquired by GM in 2016. Valued at over $14B.', 'Dropbox is a global collaboration platform where content is created, accessed, and shared. Market cap: over $10 Billion.', 'Coinbase is a digital currency wallet and platform where merchants and consumers can transact with new digital currencies like bitcoin, ethereum, and litecoin. Valued at over $8 Billion.', 'Instacart is building the best way for people anywhere in the world to shop for groceries. Valued at over $7s Billion.', 'MZ builds massive mobile games that break down linguistic and geographic barriers by uniting an unprecedented number of global players in one gaming world. They’re best known for the game "Game of War". Valued at over $5 Billion.', 'DoorDash connects customers with their favorite local and national businesses in more than 850 cities across the United States and Canada. They empower merchants to grow their businesses by offering on-demand delivery, data-driven insights, and better in-store efficiency, providing delightful experiences from door to door. Valued at over $4 Billion.', 'Zenefits provides HR solutions for the new world of work, powering people to make work move and business thrive. Valued at over $2 Billion', 'Gusto automates and simplifies payroll, benefits, and HR, all while providing expert support. Valued at about $2 Billion.', 'Reddit is home to thousands of communities, endless conversation, and authentic human connection. Acquired by Conde Nast in 2006. Valued at over $1 Billion.', 'PagerDuty is the leading digital ops management platform for businesses. They empower DevOps, IT operations, support, security, and business leaders to turn any signal into insight and real-time action across any operational use case. Valued at over $1 Billion.', 'Docker is a modern platform for all applications, giving developers and IT the freedom to build, manage and secure business-critical applications without the fear of technology or infrastructure lock-in. Valued at over $1 Billion.', 'Ginkgo Bioworks is a biotech company that designs custom microbes for customers across multiple markets. Valued at over $1 Billion.', 'Rappi is an on-demand delivery startup, active in Colombia, Mexico, Brazil, Chile, Uruguay and Argentina. Valued at over $1 Billion.', 'Brex is rebuilding B2B financial products, starting with a corporate card for tech companies. Valued at over $1 Billion.', 'GitLab is the first single application built from the ground up for all stages of the DevOps lifecycle for Product, Development, QA, Security, and Operations teams to work concurrently on the same project. Valued at over $1 Billion.', 'Twitch is a live streaming video platform where millions of people and thousands of interests collide in an explosion of video games, pop culture, and conversation. Acquired by Amazon in 2014.', 'Flexport moves freight globally by air, ocean, rail, and truck for the world’s leading brands. Valued at over $1 Billion.', 'Mixpanel is a user analytics platform that lets everyone in an organization deeply understand each of its users.', 'Checkr provides modern and compliant background checks for global enterprises and startups.', 'Optimizely is the leading experimentation platform, enabling businesses to deliver continuous experimentation and personalization across websites, mobile apps and connected devices.', 'LendUp provides anyone with a path to better financial health.', 'Segment provides the customer data infrastructure that businesses use to put their customers first. With Segment, companies can collect, unify, and connect their first-party data to over 200 marketing, analytics, and data warehousing tools. Over 19,000 companies across 71 countries use Segment to achieve a common understanding of their users and make customer-centric decisions.', 'uBiome allows doctors, patients, and citizen scientists to learn about the human microbiome with unprecedented accuracy and speed.', 'Memebox is an online beauty community and collection of in-house beauty brands.', 'Zapier is a web automation app. With Zapier you can build Zaps which can automate parts of your business or life.', 'Rigetti Computing is building the world’s most powerful computers to help solve humanity’s greatest problems.', 'Thalmic is developing the future of wearable technology and human-computer interaction (HCI).', 'Podium provides messaging, reviews, and insights for local business.', 'EquipmentShare is a peer-to-peer equipment rental marketplace that also offers telematics and equipment utilization services.', 'Soylent is a complete meal that contains the vitamins and nutrients your body needs.', 'PlanGrid builds construction productivity software that allows contractors and owners in commercial, heavy civil, and other industries to work together throughout the project lifecycle.', 'Sift Science is a fraud detection solution for online businesses.', 'Algolia is a powerful search-as-a-service solution, made easy to use with API clients, UI libraries, and pre-built integrations.', 'EasyPost is the simple shipping API for the UPS API, USPS API, Fedex API, DHL API, and more.', 'Amplitude is comprehensive product analytics software for web and mobile.', 'Meta bridges the gap between the virtual and the real with the world’s most immersive AR experience.', 'WePay is an integrated payments provider designed for SaaS and crowdfunding platforms. Acquired by JPMorgan Chase in 2017.', 'MemSQL is a distributed, highly-scalable SQL database that can run anywhere.', 'Weebly allows anyone to start and grow an online business with curated website templates, powerful ecommerce and integrated marketing. Acquired by Square in 2018.', 'CoreOS develops open source tools that are the fundamental building blocks of modern distributed systems. Acquired by Red Hat in 2018.', 'Vidyard is the video platform that helps businesses transform communications and drive more revenue through the strategic use of online video.', 'Clever wants to improve education through the use of technology.', 'MessageBird connects companies to their customers on billions of devices around the world.', 'Heroku is a container-based cloud Platform as a Service (PaaS). Developers use Heroku to deploy, manage, and scale modern apps. Acquired by Salesforce in 2010.', 'GOAT is the safest way to buy and sell sneakers through your mobile device.', 'The Ridecell platform provides the technology needed to run a standalone ridesharing or carsharing operation—or a hybrid service that combines both.', 'Matterport allows professionals to capture 3D walkthroughs, photography, floor plans, and VR of real-world places from one shoot.', 'Fivestars has the largest rewards program for local business.', 'Faire helps retailers find and buy unique wholesale merchandise for their stores.', 'Atrium is a full-service corporate law firm that uses technology to give startups a legal experience that is fast, transparent, and price-predictable.', 'Rescale is a cloud simulation platform that helps engineers and scientists build, compute, analyze, and scale simulations with high performance computing.', 'Lever streamlines the hiring process and simplifies the applicant tracking system, so that recruiters and hiring managers can focus on what truly matters: their candidates.', 'Front is the shared inbox for teams -- all your emails, apps, and teammates in one collaborative workspace.', 'ShipBob does e-commerce fulfillment for online stores.', 'Le Tote is a clothing rental subscription service featuring top brands.', 'OMGPOP is a developer of social games for facebook, iphone and the open web. Acquired by Zynga in 2013.', 'Axoni’s distributed ledger technology provides secure, multi-party data infrastructure with unparalleled performance.', 'Scribd is a digital library, e-book and audiobook subscription service.', 'Lob makes it possible for enterprises to programmatically send physical mail at scale.', 'Atomwise designs new molecules for the hardest targets. Its discoveries help its partners deliver better medicines faster.', 'Heap lets you automatically capture every user interaction from web, mobile, and cloud services: clicks, submits, transactions, emails, and more.', 'Hush is building the first community-driven shopping experience on your phone.', 'FutureAdvisor helps people reach their long-term financial goals by managing their savings and investments. Acquired by Blackrock in 2015.', 'SFOX is a better way to trade digital currencies, offering the best price and deepest liquidity with a single point of access to global cryptocurrency markets.', 'InfluxData provides the leading time series platform to instrument, observe, learn and automate any system, application and business process across a variety of use cases.', 'Bitmovin develops software to solve complex problems in video streaming.', 'Boom is building Supersonic passenger jets.', 'ZeroCater delivers personalized local office catering and snacks services for your office.', 'Rainforest is helping rethink QA and bring it into today’s era of continuous delivery.', 'SmartAsset is a financial technology company aiming to provide the best personal finance advice on the web.', 'Embark develops self-driving semi trucks.', 'Razorpay is the only payment gateway for India which allows businesses to accept, process and disburse payments with ease.', 'Qventus optimizes decisions in hospitals in real time to reduce costs, improve quality and experience.', 'Cloudant is a distributed database that is optimized for handling heavy workloads that are typical of large, fast-growing web and mobile apps. Acquired by IBM in 2014.', 'GrubMarket provides affordable farm-to-table food delivery. They offer a variety of organic, locally-sourced food and produce.', 'Codecademy is an online platform that offers free coding classes in 12 different programming languages.', 'Automatic’s app and plug-in car adapter turns just about any car into a connected car. Acquired by SiriusXM in 2017.', 'Ironclad builds modern contract management and workflow automation.', 'FarmLogs is farming software designed to help farmers execute their production and grain marketing decisions.', 'Caviar lets you get delivery or pickup from the best restaurants in your neighborhood. Acquired by Square in 2014.', 'HackerRank is a technology hiring platform that is the standard for assessing developer skills for over 1,000 companies around the world.', 'Nurx offers a safe, easy solution for getting your birth control and PrEP.', 'Function of Beauty offers personalized hair care based on your hair type & hair goals.', 'Gigster is the fastest and easiest way to build custom software solutions.', 'Goldbelly is a curated marketplace for gourmet food & food gifts, featuring America’s most legendary foods.', 'BuildZoom helps you find the perfect contractor for any job – commercial or residential.', 'People.ai builds AI-powered tools that automatically capture all sales activity to drive intelligent sales management and marketing accountability.', 'inDinero builds accounting software and data for small businesses.', 'Firebase is a mobile and web application development platform. Acquired by Google in 2014.', 'Genius brings music intelligence to the masses.', 'Science Exchange is a marketplace for scientific research. They let scientists outsource their research and development to scientific institutions.', 'Thread helps anyone dress well with the help of a personal stylist.', 'The Muse helps job seekers find the best companies.', 'An analytics platform that lets you see inside companies.', 'Scale Labs provides human-powered high quality results for AI applications.', 'Strikingly is a website builder that allows the user, with little or no development experience, to create mobile optimized websites within minutes.', 'Quality local and national sports coverage from an all-star team of writers.', 'HelloSign’s digital workflow platform – which includes eSignature, digital workflow, and electronic fax solutions — helps over 75,000 companies and millions of people do business faster.', 'GoCardless is reinventing recurring payments by building a global network on top of bank debit systems. NOTE: we accidentally ommitted GoCardless from the orginal list. Correctly ranked, they would be #71.']
